text.tspan: Minnesota's voter turnout still leads the national pack
Many states across the country saw massive boosts in voter turnout compared to ​
the last presidential election. And while Minnesota's already-high turnout didn't rise ​
as much, it maintained its best-in-nation status.
COMPARING ELIGIBLE VOTER TURNOUT FROM 2016 TO 2020
